6z" fill-rule=3D"evenodd"></path></svg></a>Impact</h3>
<p>This vulnerability will lead to a permanent loss of funds if a Xnet call=
 has <code>value &gt; 0</code> and the call has failed on the destination. =
Additionally, receipts will never be handled on destination subnets.</p>
<h3 style=3D"position:relative;" id=3D"recommended-mitigation-steps-2"><a c=
