</a>Proof of Concept</h3>
<p>Let=E2=80=99s go over the following scenario:</p>
<ul>
<li>115 releases to be processed, 100 of them available to claim at the cur=
rent release time.</li>
<li><code>compact</code> function is called, <code>i =3D startIdx =3D 0</co=
de>, <code>newLength =3D length =3D 115</code>.</li>
<li><code>compact</code> processes the 100 available releases, the loop bre=
aks and this is executed:</li>
</ul>
<pre data-index=3D"41" data-language=3D"solidity" class=3D"grvsc-container =
dark-default-dark"><code class=3D"grvsc-code"><span class=3D"grvsc-line"><s=
