<p>As it is observed in the code, there are no checks to see if <code>msg.s=
ender</code> is allowed to create a new subnet under the gateway or not. Th=
is can be exploited to drain all of the funds in the gateway actor contract=
.</p>
<h3 style=3D"position:relative;" id=3D"exploit-1"><a class=3D"anchor before=
