<p>The vulnerable functions are <code>LibStaking::withdrawWithConfirm()</co=
de> and <code>LibStaking::depositWithConfirm()</code>. </p>
<p>When the subnet is not yet bootstrapped and a validator has joined the s=
ubnet and staked funds, <code>LibStaking::depositWithConfirm()</code> does =
not update the weight of the validator if he increased his stake by calling=
 <code>addStake()</code>. This will lead to the validator having an outdate=
d weight (less than the weight he should have).</p>
