t</h3>
<p>The <code>GatewayManagerFacet.register</code> function does not properly=
 validate the total <code>Filecoin (FIL)</code> value provided when registe=
ring a new subnet. It accepts two separate parameters =E2=80=93 <code>genes=
isCircSupply</code> (genesis circulating supply) and <code>collateral</code=
> =E2=80=93 and credits both to the new subnet independently against the sa=
me deposit. In the code, the subnet=E2=80=99s circulating supply and stake =
collateral are set separately without any check that their sum equals the F=
IL sent or available.</p>
<p>In <code>GatewayManagerFacet.register()</code>, there are two separate <=
code>lock</code> calls:</p>
<pre data-index=3D"57" data-language=3D"solidity" class=3D"grvsc-container =
dark-default-dark"><code class=3D"grvsc-code"><span class=3D"grvsc-line"><s=
