<p>The <code>AssetHelper.lock()</code> function for native assets only chec=
ks <code>msg.value</code> against the individual value being locked:</p>
<pre data-index=3D"58" data-language=3D"solidity" class=3D"grvsc-container =
dark-default-dark"><code class=3D"grvsc-code"><span class=3D"grvsc-line"><s=
pan class=3D"grvsc-source"><span class=3D"mtk15">if</span><span class=3D"mt=
k1"> (</span><span class=3D"mtk12">asset</span><span class=3D"mtk1">.</span=
