<p><em>Submitted by <a href=3D"https://code4rena.com/audits/2025-02-recall/=
submissions/S-202">kodyvim</a>, also found by <a href=3D"https://code4rena.=
com/audits/2025-02-recall/submissions/S-44">hecker_trieu_tien</a></em></p>
<p>Subnets using <code>permissionMode.collateral</code> uses staked collate=
ral to determine validators power. Validators can stake and unstake their c=
ollateral. </p>
<p>When a subnet gets bootstrapped (i.e. reached the <code>minActivationCol=
lateral</code> to activate the subnet) validators unstaking requires the re=
quest to be recorded which would later be confirmed by submission of checkp=
oint.</p>
